{"tid":942230,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Legal High》再曝新陣容　資深演員蔡貞安確定參演！","createTime":"2018-12-15T13:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T09:47:17.000Z","uid":3747,"like":2,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d57fc6633dada9837d07fbf98bbacc2d44e6e999","tid":942230,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"繼主演晉久、徐恩秀後，JTBC 將翻拍的《Legal High》（律政狂人）又公開了令人期待的新陣容！<br />\n<br />\nJTBC 電視台今天（12 日）宣布演員蔡貞安將在劇中飾演主角所屬事務所的競爭對手「B&amp;G 法律事務所」旗下律師閔珠晶，與尹博、鄭尙勳攜手構成和主角晉久、徐恩秀競爭的陣營。<br />\n<br />\n韓版《Legal High》描寫勝訴率 100% 的律師高泰林（晉久　飾，고태림）和擁有 100% 正義感的律師徐在仁（徐恩秀　飾，서재인），以截然不同的性格挑戰殺氣騰騰又充滿笑料的法律喜劇。<br />\n<br />\n出道已經超過 20 年的蔡貞安曾演過《咖啡王子 1 號店》、《該隱與亞伯》、《當男人戀愛時》、《龍八夷》、《金裝律師》⋯⋯等電視劇，在《純情漫畫》、《兩個戀愛》等電影中也能看見她的身影，多變的靈活演技令人印象深刻。 <br />\n<br />\n另一方面，韓版《Legal High》預定在 2019 年 2 月開播。"},{"pid":"3c56214d30c8ad1d2cc8cd0594340e794818a460","tid":942230,"uid":62294,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母以為Legal High出第三季 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76981fa82e75256c9b2bcf21e546db9acf47bb5a","tid":942230,"uid":48791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c56214d30c8ad1d2cc8cd0594340e794818a460","tid":942230,"uid":62294,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母以為Legal High出第三季 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母以為Legal High出第三季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fe83012a7d7628104b8a343c12bc81ccfd1f08","tid":942230,"uid":219529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84df37da70988ab68577a53cceac937c2d89b345","tid":942230,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c56214d30c8ad1d2cc8cd0594340e794818a460","tid":942